meta.name: description
meta.content: MaryMagdalene - Exploring Medieval Mary Magdalene (and More) Online Project Description The goal of this project is of a twofold nature: in terms of research results, it will create an interactive online edition of a medieval Mary Magdalene legend transmitted in the Lower Rhine area; in terms of teaching practice, it will train graduate and undergraduate students in palaeography, editing, and coding.

type="person" nymRef="Lazarus"><choice><orig>l</orig><reg type="capit" resp="editor">L</reg></choice>azarus</name> vnd er was <lb facs="#S_350r_a_12"/>der<pc resp="editor">,</pc>
wylcher vnser here vff erwecket <lb facs="#S_350r_a_13"/>van dem dode<pc resp="editor">,</pc> da er vyer dage
doit <lb facs="#S_350r_a_14"/>jn dem grabe hait <choice><abbr>gelege̅</abbr><expan>gelegen</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab>
die kynder yr <lb facs="#S_350r_a_16"/><choice><orig>jre</orig><corr type="repit" resp="editor"></corr></choice>vederliches erbe<pc resp="editor">.</pc>
<name type="place" nymRef="Jerusalem"><choice><abbr>jhrlm͂</abbr><expan>Jherusalem</expan></choice></name> <lb facs="#S_350r_a_18"/>vnd er ubet sich yn
<rdg wit="N" corresp="#N">word</rdg><rdg wit="B1" corresp="#B1">word</rdg><rdg wit="D" corresp="D">word</rdg></app></corr>
<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Vnd yre deyl <lb facs="#S_350v_a_8"/>was das <choice><abbr>stetgy̅</abbr><expan>stetgyn</expan></choice>
<choice><orig>vnd</orig><reg type="capit" resp="editor">Vnd</reg></choice> was yre vber <choice><abbr>verlyebn̅</abbr><expan>verlyeben</expan></choice> <lb facs="#S_350v_a_10"/>van yrer
Alle yre gut vnd <lb facs="#S_350v_a_15"/><choice><abbr>rentte̅</abbr><expan>rentten</expan></choice> bracht sie zo yn
<pb edRef="#S" facs="#S_351r"/> <lb facs="#S_351r_a_1"/>want sie was also houerdich van
yn suberlicheit yn edel<lb facs="#S_351r_a_4"/>heit vnd yn rychheit<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Auch was sie <lb/>also
<lb facs="#S_351r_a_5"/><choice><abbr>cleytdere̅</abbr><expan>cleytderen</expan></choice> vnd myt zyert<lb facs="#S_351r_a_6"/>heit yrs lychams<pc
resp="editor">.</pc> Sie was auch sere <lb facs="#S_351r_a_7"/>gyrich yn <choice><abbr>tzijtliche̅</abbr><expan>tzijtlichen</expan></choice>
>:</pc> gut<pc resp="editor">,</pc> ere <lb facs="#S_351r_a_8"/>vnd woilluste der werelt<pc resp="editor"
>.</pc> Auch <lb facs="#S_351r_a_9"/>was sie vnkusche myt <choice><abbr>wortte̅</abbr><expan>wortten</expan></choice> vnd <lb facs="#S_351r_a_10"/>myt
also <choice><abbr>dz</abbr><expan>daz</expan></choice> sie yre gut ge<lb facs="#S_351r_a_11"/>ruchte vnd
</choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> <lb facs="#S_351v_a_2"/>Aber yre lyebe suster <name type="person"
<lb facs="#S_351v_a_6"/>Der lerer <name type="person" nymRef="Pseudo_Isidore">Ysiderus</name>, der dyeße
yre schones haire vnd sie <lb facs="#S_351v_a_14"/>zieret <choice><abbr>yre̅</abbr><expan>yren</expan></choice> lycham<pc
resp="editor">.</pc> Da sprache zo <lb facs="#S_351v_a_15"/>yre <name type="person" nymRef="Martha"
dyne schone sele<pc resp="editor">,</pc> die da <lb facs="#S_351v_a_18"/><choice><abbr>geschaiffn̅</abbr><expan>geschaiffen</expan></choice>
lycham hait schult van der selen<pc resp="editor">,</pc> <lb facs="#S_352r_a_4"/><choice><abbr>vn̅</abbr><expan>vnd</expan></choice>
gedencke<pc resp="editor">,</pc> das dyne schone lycham<pc resp="editor">,</pc> <lb facs="#S_352r_a_5"/><choice><orig>D</orig><reg type="capit" resp="editor">d</reg></choice>
en du zyerst myt gultde vnd myt <lb facs="#S_352r_a_6"/>sylber<pc resp="editor">,</pc>

<choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice> <lb facs="#S_352r_a_7"/><choice><orig><choice><abbr>ey̅</abbr><expan>eyn</expan></choice></orig><corr resp="editor"></corr></choice> spyße der worme<pc resp="editor">.</pc><pc resp="editor">"</pc>
Da antwert <lb facs="#S_352r_a_8"/><name type="person" nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">Maria</name> vnd
<lb facs="#S_352r_a_9"/>na dem das ich so suberlich byn an dem <lb facs="#S_352r_a_10"/>lycham vnd yn rycheit
ich dich<pc resp="editor">,</pc> syst zofreden vnd <lb facs="#S_352r_a_12"/>laiße mych <choice><abbr>my̅</abbr><expan>myn</expan></choice>
gut verzeren myt freu<lb facs="#S_352r_a_13"/>den vnd myt den <choice><abbr>lyebhauere̅</abbr><expan>lyebhaueren</expan></choice> dyeßer
<corr><app><lem type="conjecture-supplied"><supplied resp="editor" source="B1 N K1 D">werelt</supplied></lem>
<rdg wit="B1" corresp="#B1">word</rdg><rdg wit="N" corresp="#N">word</rdg><rdg wit="K1" corresp="#K1">word</rdg><rdg wit="D" corresp="#D">word</rdg></app></corr>
</choice><pc resp="editor">.</pc> <lb facs="#S_352r_a_14"/>Vnd laiße vns nuͮ froeliche <choice><abbr>syn̅e</abbr><expan>synne</expan></choice>
myt <lb facs="#S_352r_a_15"/><choice><abbr>ey̅ander</abbr><expan>eynander</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">,</pc> wer weyße wie lange<pc resp="editor">.</pc>
nymRef="Mary_Magdalene">Maria</name> zo huyße vnd <lb facs="#S_352r_a_17"/><name type="person" nymRef="Martha"

da froelich<pc resp="editor">.</pc> Vnd dar zo wart <lb facs="#S_352v_a_4"/>auch
<lb facs="#S_352v_a_5"/>Vnd sye <choice><abbr>qua̅</abbr><expan>quam</expan></choice> auch dar myt groißer <lb facs="#S_352v_a_6"/>koistlicheit vnd zyerheit yres

<choice><abbr>nachtte̅</abbr><expan>nachtten</expan></choice><pc resp="editor">,</pc> also das sie nauwe die
<choice><abbr>moichte̅</abbr><expan>moichten</expan></choice> van groißer <lb facs="#S_352v_a_11"/>froelicheit vnd wyltdicheit<pc resp="editor">.</pc></ab>
<choice><orig>Ja</orig><corr resp="editor">Da</corr></choice> zo <lb facs="#S_352v_a_12"/>dyeßer zijt vername yre suster<pc resp="editor">,</pc> das <lb facs="#S_352v_a_13"/>vnser lyeber

><choice><orig>m</orig><reg type="capit" resp="editor">M</reg></choice>arttylla</name><pc resp="editor">,</pc> yre mayt<pc resp="editor">,</pc> des

<choice><abbr>vn̅</abbr><expan>vnd</expan></choice> fragt <lb facs="#S_353v_a_4"/>sie<pc resp="editor">,</pc> wie iß werre<pc resp="editor"
